comment_data.body:
I had the same issue and @dithmer post fixed it. Point to the global install of Typescript, in my case the option looked like this 
```lua
init_options = {
    typescript = {
        tsdk = "/usr/local/lib/node_modules/typescript/lib"
    }
}
```
